body:
Update Gradle and gradlew, the IntelliJ and Kotlin plugins for Gradle, and define a build spec for 2022.2 EAP that uses LATEST_EAP_SNAPSHOT to compile and build the Flutter plugin.

This isn't currently working. Forms do not display, which breaks things like settings, new project creation, and a few other things.

Fixes #6219

comment_data.body: Is this base version going to change over time? Not sure if it matters.
It will become something different when the EAP version is released as stable.
